Informal Settlements in Nairobi

I created the following visuals for the IDRC Project 108242 - Unlocking the Powerty Penalty and up-scaling the Resepect for Rights in Kenyas Informal Settlemens at Strathmore Universiy in Nairobi, Kenia. They give insights into two informal settlements in Nairobi - Kiandutu and Sepu - and how they compare regarding key socio-economic figures.
